```

This is called when the skb is finally freed. But note: after a successful recvmsg (consume), `unix_detach_fds` is called which sets `UNIXCB(skb).fp = NULL`. So when `unix_destruct_scm` is called later, `UNIXCB(skb).fp` is NULL and it skips the call.

